      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="preserves-link-equity-across-versions"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>When external sites link to your English page, that link equity needs to benefit your other language versions too. Hreflang tells Google that all versions belong together. Signals like backlinks and domain authority flow across the entire hreflang set.</p></div></div>
