    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="can-i-use-hreflang-with-a-single-language-site"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>If your site has only 1 language and targets only 1 country, you do not need hreflang. It only matters when you have multiple versions of the same content for different languages or regions. A single-language site benefits more from <a href="/blog/on-page-seo-guide/">on-page SEO</a> and <a href="/blog/schema-markup-seo-guide/">schema markup</a>.</p></div></div>
  </div>
