      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="does-bing-support-hreflang-tags"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Bing uses the <code>content-language</code> HTTP header and <code>meta</code> tag instead of hreflang. Bing does not officially support hreflang. If you target Bing users, add the <code>content-language</code> meta tag alongside your hreflang tags. Google ignores <code>content-language</code>, so you need both for full coverage.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
